  "title": "Structural and kinetic basis for heightened immunogenicity of T cell vaccines.",
  "journal": "The Journal of experimental medicine",
  "year": 2005,
  "authors": "Chen JL, Stewart-Jones G, Bossi G, Lissin NM, Wooldridge L, Choi EM, Held G, Dunbar PR, Esnouf RM, Sami M, Boulter JM, Rizkallah P, Renner C, Sewell A, van der Merwe PA, Jakobsen BK, Griffiths G, Jones EY, Cerundolo V."
